==芒康邦达仓==
[[芒康县|芒康县]]的邦达仓是邦达仓家族在芒康的故居，位于[[芒康县|芒康县]]交呷古秀邦达村。邦达仓家族便起源于今[[芒康县|芒康县]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.changdutravel.com/news/artc_show.php?id=183&colId=35 |title=邦达仓故居，昌都旅游信息网，于2013-08-07查阅 |accessdate=2013-08-07 |archive-date=2013-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531020342/http://www.changdutravel.com/news/artc_show.php?id=183&colId=35 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

